F(x)=\sum_{k=0}^n x^k=\frac{1-x^n}{1-x}\iff F'(x)=\sum_{k=0}^n kx^{k-1}=\sum_{k=0}^n kx^k-\sum_{k=0}^n x^k=\sum_{k=0}^n kx^k-F(x)
f(x)=\sum_{k=0}^n kx^k=F(x)+F'(x)=\frac{1-x^n}{1-x}+\left(\frac{1-x^n}{1-x}\right)_x'=\ldots
